                         1. PROJECT OVERVIEW
================================================================================

Project Name: Shop Management System

Description:
A 100% Offline Progressive Web App (PWA) for shopkeepers to manage
inventory and track daily sales without internet connectivity.

Type: Offline-First Web Application
Platform: Cross-platform (Web, Desktop, Mobile)
Architecture: Single Page Application (SPA)

Key Highlights:
- Works 100% offline
- Installable as desktop/mobile app
- No server required
- Data stored locally in browser
- Customer-wise sales grouping
- Print, WhatsApp, SMS sharing

